  setupName: Top-Down 2D Arena Proof
  summary: Local Sprite2D pawn movement, top-down camera bounds, projectile firing,
    auto-collected pickups, scoring, and a score HUD.
  runtimeCapabilities:
  - capabilityFamily: 1
    patternDefinition: {fileID: 11400000, guid: eb4719ede64f07449bdd90db6d875c7e, type: 2}
    requiredForFirstProof: 1
    creatorNotes: First prove the pawn can spawn and move inside camera bounds.
  - capabilityFamily: 4
    patternDefinition: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c886c23cae665de4a985afd675bffc01, type: 2}
    requiredForFirstProof: 1
    creatorNotes: Then prove primary attack can fire an authored projectile prefab.
  - capabilityFamily: 8
    patternDefinition: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1e93f00a018b1c74e9f1adbb998e5f67, type: 2}
    requiredForFirstProof: 1
    creatorNotes: Finally prove pickup awards can drive the score HUD.
  runtimePatterns:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: eb4719ede64f07449bdd90db6d875c7e, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: c886c23cae665de4a985afd675bffc01, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1e93f00a018b1c74e9f1adbb998e5f67, type: 2}
  setupNotes: Open the scene, inspect the bootstrap/session assets, press Play, move
